snippet.title: Croak Reveal Trailer - Future Games Show Gamescom 2024
snippet.description:
A world premiere trailer revealed Croak, a cartoon platformer from developers and animators with previous credits on Cuphead and Rick and Morty. It's coming soon to PC.

https://www.youtube.com/@FutureGamesShow

#croak #FutureGamesShow #FGS #futuregamesshow2024 #gamescom
